  {
    "text": "Demonstration of DOCX support in calibre",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "ods",
      "sheetName": "Sheet1"
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "calibre",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "ods",
      "sheetName": "Sheet1"
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "There is support for images, tables, lists, footnotes, endnotes, links, dropcaps and various types of text and paragraph level formatting.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "ods",
      "sheetName": "Sheet1"
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "“Add Books” Convert”. “OK”",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "ods",
      "sheetName": "Sheet1"
    }
  },
